<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> nehst <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz wir <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> graf <expan>Joh<ex>ann</ex></expan> von
                        Wertheim <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> tun <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan>, also tun
                        wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> zu <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz
                        wir <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Wertheim
                            <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> getan und uns sein gnade
                                <expan>wid<ex>er</ex>umb</expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat, als ir an der
                                <expan>eingesloss<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>abschr<ex>ift</ex></expan> seins briefs wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan> werdet, da mag sich ewr
                                <expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> nach <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        zu <expan>richt<ex>en</ex></expan>. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Dionisii.</ab>
